## Cursor Config Files
- `.cursor/mcp.json` – Registered MCP server targets `dist/index.js`.
- `.cursor/cli.json` – Defines default cwd, env, and safe commands for `cursor agent`.
- `.cursor/modes.json` – Community modes for Persona Ops, Memory Ops, and Frontend Runway workflows.

